title: DuneCD - The original Dune PC game (dune.zip - fixed)
description:
I got this from another torrent, but one of the components in the ZIP archive was corrupted.  I found that component separately, and fixed the ZIP archive.  I am re-seeding this fixed version, for your edification.

It is an oldie RPG of sorts, with VGA graphics; you will probably need to get DOSBox to run this game.  But never mind, this is a classic!
